==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Reduvid
<hw>Red"u*vid</hw> <pr>(r?d"?*v?d)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>reduvia</ets> a hangnail.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Any
hemipterous insect of the genus <gen>Redivius</gen>, or family
<fam>Reduvidae</fam>. They live by sucking the blood of other insects,
and some species also attack man.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Redweed</ent>⟦br⟧
